00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:41,460
I'm much better and don't want to
stay cooped up in the house.

263
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,940
Thanks for picking
the Worry-free Immortal Fruit for me.

264
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:49,110
Don't take such risks next time.

265
00:19:50,070 --> 00:19:51,900
Perhaps it's difficult to be worry-free.

266
00:19:54,070 --> 00:19:55,590
Is this Miss Wan Yue?

267
00:19:58,440 --> 00:20:02,390
She taught me how to make a sculpture
with a knife.

268
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:07,310
Completing it bit by bit
makes it more precious.

269
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:15,590
It's a pity that such days are too short.

270
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:18,900
You knew that Miss Wan Yue
was a mortal,

271
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:25,110
and the laws of heaven and earth
were so cruel.

272
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:30,790
Why did you have to...

273
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:32,420
Have to force it?

274
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:43,790
It's not what I meant.

275
00:20:46,070 --> 00:20:49,830
It's just that feelings arose without control,
and I couldn't bear to part with her.

276
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:51,790
Yes,

277
00:20:54,510 --> 00:20:56,980
this is something
that cannot be controlled.

278
00:20:57,920 --> 00:21:03,390
I just didn't expect
that he's so far from me,

279
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:08,310
so far that I cannot reach
no matter how hard I try.

280
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:13,660
It won't change anything
even if I force it.

281
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:14,800
Yin,

282
00:21:15,270 --> 00:21:17,220
you know Jin's identity now?

283
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:20,660
So you know it all along.

284
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:25,150
Only the chief and I know it
in the entire Daze Mountain.

285
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:28,430
Yin,

286
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:30,900
since you know it's an extravagant hope,

287
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:34,460
then cut off this impossible attachment.

288
00:21:36,110 --> 00:21:36,980
Yin,

289
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:41,310
I can't bear to see you fall into
the same situation as Wan Yue.

290
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:47,550
I thought I could face life and death together
with her and resist everything.

291
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:53,350
But I forgot that the weakest would
bear the worst result.

292
00:21:54,550 --> 00:21:58,260
I suffered the Thunder Punishment,
but I had my immortal body protecting me.

293
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:00,830
But what about Wan Yue?

294
00:22:02,270 --> 00:22:08,630
She exhausted everything she had
and still perished without hope.

295
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:14,070
Our love violates the forbidden rules
of the Immortal Realm.

296
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:18,870
But why only Wan Yue bears
the bitter consequences?

297
00:22:20,350 --> 00:22:23,590
Yin, don't fall into such a situation.

298
00:22:24,790 --> 00:22:26,420
You can't bear the consequences.

299
00:22:26,420 --> 00:22:28,460
Miss Wan Yue said she doesn't regret it,

300
00:22:29,030 --> 00:22:30,500
so I won't regret it either.

301
00:22:30,830 --> 00:22:34,110
Yin, don't let yourself get entangled
in such obsession.

302
00:23:00,750 --> 00:23:04,460
I'm sure you have heard
what Yin said just now.

303
00:23:06,030 --> 00:23:08,420
I didn't expect Yin could be this stubborn.

304
00:23:09,110 --> 00:23:12,350
Lady Hong Chou won't let it go.
She'll try to kill her again.

305
00:23:13,510 --> 00:23:17,390
We can only have Jin and Yin
separated as soon as possible.

306
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:22,220
They'll both be safe
when they aren't together.

307
00:23:26,240 --> 00:23:27,080
Xian Shan,

308
00:23:29,750 --> 00:23:30,830
you want to see me?

309
00:23:32,240 --> 00:23:33,080
Jin,

310
00:23:33,790 --> 00:23:35,630
you won the Trial Assembly

311
00:23:35,630 --> 00:23:37,810
and you should've filled
in a position in the Heavenly Palace.

312
00:23:37,810 --> 00:23:41,630
And now, the Heavenly Palace is in need
of help for the Spiritual Trigram Assembly.

313
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:44,220
You are thus summoned
to head the War God Hall.

314
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:45,500
So sudden.

315
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:50,280
Alright.

316
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:53,980
I've looked everywhere in Daze Mountain
and couldn't find any trace of the parasol tree.

317
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:58,830
There are a lot of ancient books in
the Heavenly Palace. Maybe I can find a clue.

318
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:01,460
Then pack your stuff and head off.

319
00:24:01,830 --> 00:24:05,460
Xian Shan, can I take Yin with me?

320
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:10,560
Jin,

321
00:24:11,110 --> 00:24:13,070
Yin is no longer your contract spirit beast.

322
00:24:13,310 --> 00:24:16,030
There's no position for her
in the Palace. You can't break the rules.

323
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:18,590
Jin,

324
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:22,420
the Heavenly Palace already
went easy on us for Xian Zhu's matter.

325
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:26,030
Do not do anything out of line
and insult the Heavenly Palace again.

326
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:27,800
Don't be late.

327
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:28,870
Off you go.

328
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:33,280
Xian Shan,

329
00:24:34,750 --> 00:24:37,790
Yin has been a little down lately.

330
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:41,310
Help me take care of her if you could.

331
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:43,110
Don't let her stay inside all the time.

332
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:44,240
Tell her that after I come back

333
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:48,550
from the Heavenly Palace,
I'll bring her a lot of gifts.

334
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:51,760
Go ahead.

335
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:05,180
Yin, here.

336
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:08,620
Last time you brought back some dirt
from Ningyun Mountain.

337
00:25:08,620 --> 00:25:11,100
We took the Spirit Swift Dog to search for it
following the scent of the dirt

338
00:25:11,110 --> 00:25:12,700
and finally found
the location of the mountain.

339
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:15,520
It's right here.

340
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:19,790
It sits in the Illusion Forest on the border
between the Immortal and Demon Realms.

341
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:25,150
Great.

342
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,750
We finally found Ningyun Mountain.

343
00:25:28,030 --> 00:25:29,140
Thank you, Xian Shan.

344
00:25:29,510 --> 00:25:31,110
I'll go there right now.

345
00:25:31,290 --> 00:25:32,190
Go ahead.

346
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:36,550
By the way,

347
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:39,700
I went to look for Jin today,
but I didn't see him.

348
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,310
Do you know where he is?

349
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:43,700
Jin has left for the Heavenly Palace.

350
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:46,700
He won't come back soon.

351
00:25:49,550 --> 00:25:51,420
Is he avoiding me?

352
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:56,660
Yin, Jin wants you
to take good care of yourself.

353
00:26:01,070 --> 00:26:01,910
I will.

354
00:26:04,030 --> 00:26:06,150
Then I'm leaving.

355
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:36,310
Xian Shan asked me
and some other fellow brothers

356
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:38,740
to go with you to the mountain
and help you assart the place.

357
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:39,700
Why did you refuse?

358
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:42,980
You'll be bored going there alone,
and you'll have no one to take care of you.

359
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:45,220
Who said I'm alone?

360
00:26:45,750 --> 00:26:47,940
I have Yu with me.
She'll keep me company.

361
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:53,550
I'm going to Ningyun Mountain
to clear my mind as well.

362
00:26:53,750 --> 00:26:56,030
Please thank our fellow brothers for me.

363
00:26:57,310 --> 00:26:58,550
Jiu went back to the Demon Realm,

364
00:26:58,720 --> 00:27:00,340
Jin left for the Heavenly Palace,

365
00:27:00,340 --> 00:27:02,310
and you are going to Ningyun Mountain.

366
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:06,350
Without you guys,
Daze Mountain is quiet and no fun.

367
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:08,110
Jiu went back to the Demon Realm?

368
00:27:08,590 --> 00:27:09,530
The day before yesterday,

369
00:27:09,530 --> 00:27:12,100
I saw him walk
out of his room looking sad.

370
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:13,260
I asked him where he was going,

371
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:17,700
he said he's a demon, and he can't get used
to staying in the Immortal Realm,

372
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,870
and then he took a leap and flew away.

373
00:27:20,350 --> 00:27:24,030
Why did he leave without saying goodbye?

374
00:27:24,590 --> 00:27:26,070
After all, this place is not his home.

375
00:27:26,550 --> 00:27:29,860
But, Yin, don't forget that Daze Mountain
is always your home.

376
00:27:29,860 --> 00:27:31,900
That's also what Xian Shan
asked me to tell you.

377
00:27:45,420 --> 00:27:46,700
(The Demon Realm)

378
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:07,500
What's the big deal?

379
00:28:08,790 --> 00:28:11,420
Beauties are everywhere.

380
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:15,940
It's not like I have one choice only.

381
00:29:02,030 --> 00:29:02,870
Get out.

382
00:29:03,270 --> 00:29:04,110
Get out.

383
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:05,870
Get out, all of you!

384
00:29:13,030 --> 00:29:18,870
But, no one can replace her.

385
00:30:51,340 --> 00:30:52,820
(Ningyun Mountain, the Immortal Realm)

386
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:22,150
Yu, according to the records,

387
00:31:22,510 --> 00:31:25,740
the water of the Xuan Lake
can nurture your spiritual power.

388
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:28,790
You can hatch in no time.

389
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:55,520
Qing Yi.

390
00:31:56,030 --> 00:31:56,980
Jiu.

391
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:03,790
What brings you back here so quickly?

392
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:05,500
Lower your voice.

393
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:07,390
Let me ask you.

394
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:11,630
How is it going with the two?

395
00:32:12,550 --> 00:32:13,390
Who?

396
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:15,460
What are you talking about?

397
00:32:16,310 --> 00:32:17,660
Yin and Gu Jin.

398
00:32:18,110 --> 00:32:19,740
Yin and Gu Jin... They...

399
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:25,790
Do I have to burn the Disciple Roll

400
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:30,150
to break the marriage contract,
and then win Yin's heart over?

401
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:31,280
Hold on a sec.

402
00:32:31,830 --> 00:32:34,500
What are you talking about?
I'm confused.

403
00:32:34,790 --> 00:32:38,550
Jin and Yin, one is in the Heavenly Palace
right now, and the other is in Ningyun Mountain.

404
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:40,230
They are so far away from each other.

405
00:32:40,230 --> 00:32:41,790
How could they make a marriage contract?

406
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:45,460
They didn't?

407
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:49,740
Yin found Ningyun Mountain?

408
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:51,590
Where is it?

409
00:33:48,140 --> 00:33:51,780
(War God Hall, Heavenly Palace)

410
00:34:19,670 --> 00:34:21,700
I wonder what Yin is doing right now.

411
00:34:28,070 --> 00:34:28,910
Yin.

412
00:34:31,670 --> 00:34:32,510
- Yin.
- Jiu.

413
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:33,740
What are you doing here?

414
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:36,150
So, this is Ningyun Mountain.

415
00:34:36,850 --> 00:34:38,050
Beautiful, isn't it?

416
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:41,840
The mountain is, the lake is.

417
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:45,740
Everything here is beautiful.

418
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:47,300
Of course it is.

419
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:50,380
Ningyun Mountain has remained
undisturbed for tens of thousands of years.

420
00:34:50,380 --> 00:34:53,740
Look, the spiritual energy
is abundant in this place.

421
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:56,700
It makes the mountain
so otherworldly and marvelous.

422
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:58,550
Look.

423
00:34:58,840 --> 00:34:59,680
Yu.

424
00:34:59,920 --> 00:35:01,400
As soon as Yu gets in the Xuan Lake,

425
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:03,780
the spiritual energy gathers
around her right away.

426
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:07,260
Once Yu hatches,

427
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:09,590
I'll have a little sister.

428
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:15,100
At that time, Ningyun Mountain
will be even more wonderful.

429
00:35:15,670 --> 00:35:16,510
By the way,

430
00:35:17,150 --> 00:35:18,630
I promised you

431
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:21,990
that if I find Ningyun Mountain,
I'll let you pick a place to stay.

432
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:24,580
Alright. You bet I will.

433
00:35:24,580 --> 00:35:26,990
Let me see. Where should I pick?

434
00:35:29,230 --> 00:35:30,820
Can I ask you something?

435
00:35:30,820 --> 00:35:31,740
What is it?

436
00:35:33,110 --> 00:35:36,150
When you and Yan Shuang
went about the task of the Three-life Stone,

437
00:35:37,110 --> 00:35:38,860
did you feel something unusual?

438
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:41,700
What do you mean, unusual?

439
00:35:42,030 --> 00:35:44,990
Did you develop some
short-time affection for her

440
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:50,950
under the influence of the Stone?

441
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:01,030
I...

442
00:36:01,670 --> 00:36:02,700
I guess.

443
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:04,160
You did?

444
00:36:05,030 --> 00:36:05,990
Of course.

445
00:36:07,110 --> 00:36:12,030
So, if... If we kissed or hugged at the time,

446
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:15,640
it was all fake, like a dream.

447
00:36:16,150 --> 00:36:18,260
Yin, do not take it seriously.

448
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:28,740
So, Jin was only influenced by the Stone.

449
00:36:30,510 --> 00:36:37,180
He didn't mean what he said or did.

450
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:43,380
Did you ask me that because of Gu Jin?

451
00:36:43,710 --> 00:36:44,950
Who are you guys?

452
00:36:50,110 --> 00:36:50,950
Your Lordship, you are...

453
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:53,110
I'm the Inspector of the Heavenly Palace.

454
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:54,990
The Inspector?

455
00:36:54,990 --> 00:36:57,540
The Heavenly Palace sensed movements
reappeared in Ningyun Mountain.

456
00:36:57,540 --> 00:36:58,910
I was sent here for a check.

457
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:01,590
You two, leave here right now.

458
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:04,720
It's an unclaimed place.
It belongs to whoever finds it first.

459
00:37:05,110 --> 00:37:07,630
You can't own it before you file
an application to the Heavenly Palace.

460
00:37:07,800 --> 00:37:09,710
If you don't leave,

461
00:37:09,710 --> 00:37:13,070
the Palace will send soldiers tomorrow
to make you leave.

462
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:18,820
We… We should've told him

463
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,210
that I'm a Water Divine Beast,

464
00:37:20,210 --> 00:37:21,870
and Ningyun Mountain is my home.

465
00:37:21,870 --> 00:37:22,990
That way, he wouldn't let us leave.

466
00:37:22,990 --> 00:37:24,180
No, you can't.

467
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:28,700
Do you know how many cultivators want
the spiritual core of a Water Divine Beast?

468
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:30,340
If you expose your identity,

469
00:37:30,630 --> 00:37:32,550
you'll become prey in their eyes,

470
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,380
and your life will be in danger.

471
00:37:36,070 --> 00:37:37,300
Then what should we do?

472
00:37:37,300 --> 00:37:39,480
(Blessed Cave)

473
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:41,590
Our Demon Realm never has
these many absurd rules.

474
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:47,680
Yin,

475
00:37:49,110 --> 00:37:52,580
why don't you join our demon clan?

476
00:37:52,580 --> 00:37:55,070
I'll find you a better place
than Ningyun Mountain,

477
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:59,180
and I'll be with you all the time
to protect and take care of you.

478
00:38:00,070 --> 00:38:02,430
I'm happy as long as I can see you.

479
00:38:05,150 --> 00:38:05,990
I like you.

480
00:38:06,150 --> 00:38:07,020
Are you out of your mind?

481
00:38:07,020 --> 00:38:07,860
I...

482
00:38:07,870 --> 00:38:09,580
You think I just met you?

483
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:11,510
- I...
- You just want to steal my spiritual power.

484
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:13,740
Stop talking nonsense.

485
00:38:14,190 --> 00:38:15,630
Without Ningyun Mountain,

486
00:38:16,030 --> 00:38:17,740
without the nurture of the Xuan Lake,

487
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:19,910
Yu can never hatch.

488
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:31,280
You are also here.

489
00:38:31,760 --> 00:38:33,500
Yin, I went to Daze Mountain to find you.

490
00:38:33,500 --> 00:38:35,150
They said you found a new place to stay.

491
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:38,990
So, I brought you some fine wine
and gifts to celebrate.

492
00:38:39,190 --> 00:38:41,320
I saw the Xuan Lake
is covered by spiritual energy,

493
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,670
and I figured it must be your new home,

494
00:38:42,670 --> 00:38:44,300
so I came here
following the spiritual energy.

495
00:38:51,030 --> 00:38:51,870
What's wrong?

496
00:38:53,150 --> 00:38:55,660
So, you are a Water Divine Beast,

497
00:38:56,030 --> 00:38:57,950
and you can't tell people you are,

498
00:38:58,320 --> 00:39:00,860
hence, you can't be the owner
of Ningyun Mountain.

499
00:39:01,230 --> 00:39:02,550
That's what's bothering you?

500
00:39:04,070 --> 00:39:07,060
Yin told you her real identity
because you are her friend.

501
00:39:07,060 --> 00:39:08,230
You must keep it to yourself.

502
00:39:08,230 --> 00:39:09,950
I don't need you to tell me that,
stupid fox.

503
00:39:11,670 --> 00:39:13,300
Yin, don't worry.

504
00:39:13,550 --> 00:39:15,470
I will keep it a secret for you,

505
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:17,550
and I won't let anybody hurt you.

506
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:23,830
But, if you want to be the owner
of Ningyun Mountain,

507
00:39:23,830 --> 00:39:25,550
there's more than one way to do it.

508
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,070
You have an idea?

509
00:39:30,150 --> 00:39:32,610
The Heavenly Palace
is recruiting new officials right now.

510
00:39:32,610 --> 00:39:34,390
Look, you are smart and capable.

511
00:39:34,390 --> 00:39:38,150
As long as you work hard and strive
to get a promotion as a fifth-rank official,

512
00:39:38,510 --> 00:39:40,550
you'll have the right
to claim your own place.

513
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:44,280
At that time, you can easily apply
to the Heavenly Palace for the ownership

514
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:45,120
of the mountain.

515
00:39:47,960 --> 00:39:48,990
A fifth-rank official?

516
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,660
(Blessed Cave)

517
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:53,780
That's a good idea.

518
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:58,180
Gu Jin never mentioned to you
that the Heavenly Palace is recruiting?

519
00:39:58,670 --> 00:40:00,490
How could he leave you
high and dry like this?

520
00:40:00,490 --> 00:40:02,780
He's also in the Heavenly Palace.
He can take care of you.

521
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:08,910
You had to rub that in, didn't you?

522
00:40:15,860 --> 00:40:17,820
(Heavenly Palace, the Immortal Realm)

523
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:24,070
Lan Feng, I've long wanted
to have a drink with you.

524
00:40:26,110 --> 00:40:26,990
Watch your mouth.

525
00:40:29,710 --> 00:40:33,740
Your Majesty, you and my daughter are
a perfect match. I'm happy for you indeed.

526
00:40:34,190 --> 00:40:36,910
But, your marriage matters to the future
of both our families and clans.

527
00:40:37,150 --> 00:40:40,950
With all due respect,
I'll be straight with you.

528
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:42,860
Lord Hua, I'm listening.

529
00:40:43,030 --> 00:40:46,340
Although you are
the Acting Heavenly Emperor now,

530
00:40:46,550 --> 00:40:50,110
the Heavenly Empress Feng Yuan will
succeed to the throne sooner or later.

531
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:54,150
