some other time.

542
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:34,340
We'll be family in the future.

543
00:41:34,800 --> 00:41:37,990
Court business and family business
are all the same.

544
00:41:39,070 --> 00:41:40,300
That's right. Your Majesty,

545
00:41:40,710 --> 00:41:43,660
I've been obsessed
with weapons since I was little,

546
00:41:44,190 --> 00:41:46,950
