A position like this should be saved for family.

548
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:51,680
Right?

549
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:56,150
Since I'm the Acting Heavenly Emperor,
I must do things by the rules.

550
00:41:56,880 --> 00:41:59,740
The Head position matters
to the fairness of the Immortal Realm.

551
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:02,070
I can't save it for a family member.

552
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:03,990
That's understandable.

553
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:08,150
I told my father and brother many times
that Lan Feng is a just and upright man.

554
00:42:08,960 --> 00:42:12,220
