over the years, and they were all recorded.

556
00:42:16,260 --> 00:42:17,630
He won't let you down.

557
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:19,260
That's good to know.

558
00:42:20,190 --> 00:42:22,740
So, are you ready to take the office now?

559
00:42:24,190 --> 00:42:25,030
Sure.

560
00:42:25,480 --> 00:42:28,820
However, according to the rules,
you must start from being an Acting Head.

561
00:42:30,630 --> 00:42:31,630
An Acting Head?

562
00:42:34,230 --> 00:42:36,380
My brother has never served
the Heavenly Palace before.

563
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:39,550
It's good to have a buffer period.

564
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:43,590
Then, I really appreciate it, Your Majesty.

565
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:45,990
Here,

566
